</section>
<section class="block">
    <div id="what-we-do" class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
        <h5 class="section-subtitle">Video/POS Cloud-Based Integration</h5>
        <h5 class="section-subtitle" style="text-align: justify;">With more than 70 years of security video experience between them, Phil Tolle and Kevin Searight co-founded 3 Palms Intelligent Video Solutions to support the loss prevention practices of multi-site businesses. Our primary focus is to assist in the effort to identify and address incidences of theft and fraud at the Point of Sale with an existing video infrastructure.</h5>
        <p>3 Palms has partnered with Solink, Inc. to provide a Cloud-based Exception Reporting Service as the centerpiece to integrate your existing video and POS detail. Solink is installed parallel to an existing video infrastructure so that no expensive physical hardware/software re-configurations or licensing are required with an existing NVR server device. The only connectivity needed is to an open port on the PoE switch and a static IP Address assigned to the network. As a result, the current recording and camera devices remain untouched and can continue to be serviced by your existing partners.</p>
        <p>Supported by a forensic case management suite, our Clients have remote access to both on-site video as well as a minimum of one year of cloud archived storage. This provides the foundation for a forensic video/data review to supplement Loss Prevention investigations and/or Operational Training. Health monitoring options identify, notify, and minimize the downtime of their current video system; while on-line 24/7 chat support is readily available.</p>
        <p>In addition, the support of our Video Manufacturer partners affords 3 Palms the ability to provide our Clients with a cost-effective option to both supplement and support their existing video investment as needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="solutions" class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Solutions</h2>
        <h5 class="section-subtitle">Video Technology Partners</h5>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <a href="http://solinkcorp.com" target="_blank"><img src="~/Content/Images/logo_solink_transparent_white.png" width="250" height="41" class="d-inline-block align-top" alt=""></a>
                <p>Solink is a data-driven security platform that provides network solutions for the identification and reporting of fraudulent activities for the retail and financial markets. A subscription base solution, the software automatically matches in-store transactions to video and analyzes the data to identify suspicious events. Using the web or mobile app, you can access all locations remotely, search for incidents, and quickly share evidence. In addition, the solution provides management with the tools to identify additional Training opportunities. With Solink, you can dramatically reduce investigation times and know that you're keeping a close eye on your operations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <a href="https://hanwhasecurity.com" target="_blank"><img src="~/Content/Images/logo_hanwhatechwin_transparent_white.png" width="250" height="71" class="d-inline-block align-top" alt=""></a>
                <p>Hanwha Techwin America (formerly Samsung Techwin) is a precision technology company that has accumulated manufacturing expertise over 60 years of operation. Hanwha recently introduced the Wisenet line of innovative security products that include the 360° Fisheye and Multi Directional 180° cameras. Hanwha Techwin America provides products and technologies with the highest levels of performance, reliability and cost-efficiency for professional security applications.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <a href="http://specotech.com" target="_blank"><img src="~/Content/Images/logo_speco_transparent_white.png" width="250" height="64" class="d-inline-block align-top" alt=""></a>
                <p>For over fifty years, Speco Technologies has provided the latest innovations in high definition video surveillance and accessories. Speco continues to support the industry with affordable, dependable product, while delivering exceptional customer service through extensive product training and technical support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
