                <h5>Co-Founder</h5>
                <h5>36 years of industry experience</h5>
                <p>A seasoned physical security professional, Phil has served in both National Sales integration and Retail Loss Prevention leadership positions since 1982. Throughout his 15 years of Executive Loss Prevention roles with Hills Department Stores, Thalhimers, McCrory’s, Highland Superstores and Lord & Taylor, he employed a combination of team leadership and strategic planning with his support staff to achieve success in both profitability goals and objectives. These tools served him well as he made the transition into physical security systems integration as a solutions provider with Sensormatic in 1997. Continuing to serve as a Trusted Adviser for over 20 years with enterprise video leaders including Vector Security and NAVCO, Phil has continued to provide a diverse solution perspective and exemplary customer service through his unique experience as a Client and Integrator. He welcomes the opportunity for 3 Palms to be at YOUR service.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h3>Kevin Searight</h3>
                <h5>Co-Founder</h5>
                <h5>35 years of industry experience</h5>
                <p>Kevin’s diverse background in the electronic security industry affords him the expertise to consistently deliver innovative solutions and increased profitability to his customers. Areas of proficiency include: Strategic Vision, Meticulous Attention to Detail (MAD), Consultative Customer Engagement, unparalleled commitment to Customer Service and providing strong Leadership to the enterprises he has served. Kevin comes to 3 Palms Intelligent Video Solutions following a varied career as a Systems Integrator at Sensormatic, Comm-Works and Iverify as well as a Manufacturer of advanced Intelligent Video Solutions at companies including Tyco, ClickIT and Verint Video Solutions. Kevin is adept at identifying and responding to his Customers unique business needs and delivering consultative, business driven, ROI based Technology and Service Solutions that provide high value to all stakeholders. </p>
